            <div class="mainBodyText">
                <span class="fs5"><!-- OldURL: http://boards2.parentsplace.com/messages/get/pplibchristiann9/36/1/1.html -->
<p>The book of Job needed a better editor.</p>

Job feels like someone wrote all the characters and paragraphs and then assigned the speeches without regard to logic or plot. It seems like the book is about one theme and suddenlty it is about another theme altogether (or is that a moral tacked on by an editor somwhere along the line?).
<P>

Job reads like poetry, "The Saga of Job", epic poetry.
<P>

I could almost believe that many soap operas are based on the structure of Job.
<P>

Sara

