            <div class="mainBodyText">
                <span class="fs5"><!-- OldURL: http://boards2.parentsplace.com/messages/get/pplibchristiann9/36/2/1.html -->
<p>Love gives me a claim...</p>

Even when I'm not fooling anyone but myself in claiming righteousness, Love binds me. Love holds back on giving me what I deserve and gives me something greater than what I ask for.
<P>

LOL! I'm feeling pretty guilty right now and I *know* that even when I appear to the world as blessed it has NOTHING to do with my spiritual state.
<P>

I probably wouldn't read this Psalm the same way any other time.
<P>

Sara

<P>

